pr_title: O3 1314 - Update the configurations to local instance test backend for 3.X E2E test
pr_body: ## Purpose The pull request is to update configurations and readme guidance for the local instance test backend and this pull request is related to the issue ticket number [O3-1314](https://issues.openmrs.org/browse/O3-1314). ## Goals - Change the test backend to a local instance for 3.x E2E testing ## Approach 1. Update configurations for local instance test backend for 3.X E2E test 2. Update the readme guidance to set up the local environment. ### Screenshots #### Passed test (Login)

pr_title: O3-1359:Remove the unwanted 3.X test and workflows from QA framework
pr_body:
## Purpose
The pull request is to remove the unwanted 3.x test workflows, test files, and feature files from the QA framework and this pull request is related to the issue ticket number [O3-1359](https://issues.openmrs.org/browse/O3-1359)

## Goals
- Remove the tests which are not working since the issues related to the 3.X E2E testing framework.
- Update the guidelines to a workable dockerized version.

## Approach
- Remove unwanted 3.x E2E tests cases and workflows.
- Remove the existing O3 docker file.

pr_title: O3-1375: Remove 3.x related stuff from the contrib-qaframework repository
pr_body:
## Purpose 

* The purpose of this pull request is to remove the 3.x related stuff from this repository since the 3.X test will bring to a new repository. [New Repo](https://github.com/openmrs/openmrs-test-3refapp)
* Issue ticket number - [O3-1375](https://issues.openmrs.org/browse/O3-1375)
